<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Inclusion Criteria Not Met</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 10px;">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <h1 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Email subject: Inclusion criteria not met for Physiotherapy</h1>
                <p style="line-height: 1.6;"><strong>Email content:</strong></p>
                <p style="line-height: 1.6;">{{date}}</p>
                <p style="line-height: 1.6;">Hello {{name}},</p>
                <p style="line-height: 1.6;">Your answers from the Provide Physiotherapy Self-referral platform below show that you do not meet the criteria to access the service at present.</p>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" border="1" style="border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <tr>
                        <th style="padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Questions</th>
                        <th style="padding: 10px; text-align: left;">Answers</th>
                    </tr>
                    {{#each answers}}
                    <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 10px; text-align: left;">{{question}}</td>
                        <td style="padding: 10px; text-align: left;">{{answer}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </table>

                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">We recommend you visit <a href="https://providephysiotherapy.org.uk/" style="color: #0073e6; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">https://providephysiotherapy.org.uk/</a> for further support including our symptom checker and self-help advice. Also, download the getUBetter app that provides evidence-based digital self-management support for all common musculoskeletal injuries and conditions - <a href="https://www.getubetter.com/getting-started" style="color: #0073e6; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">https://www.getubetter.com/getting-started</a></p>
                
                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Alternatively, book an appointment with a First Contact Physiotherapist (FCP), a service now provided by most GP practices throughout your local area, to discuss further management of your musculoskeletal symptoms.</p>
                
                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Please contact your GP surgery to see if you have access to this service and if not, please book an appointment with your GP.</p>
                
                <p style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Please provide this information to the healthcare professional reviewing you.</p>

                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-top: 20px;">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;">
                            Kind regards,<br>
                            <strong>Smart Referral System</strong> | Provide Online Referral Service
                        </td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">
                            <img src="logo.png" alt="Smart Referral System Logo" style="max-width: 100px;">
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>


